RAIL.ST.summary: Railcare Group AB (publ) provides railway maintenance services primarily in Scandinavia and the United Kingdom. The company offers maintenance services for railway reballasting beneath tracks and switches; special transport services, including locomotives, wagons, and temporary personnel; and workshop services, such as repairs, upgrades, and regular maintenance. It also conducts construction and project transports, heavy transports, and special transports that require traffic permits; supplies locomotives, wagons, and machines; installs radio control systems and safety systems; and renovates and modifies railway vehicles. In addition, the company produces, markets, and sells engineered machines, including ballast feeder systems and snow clearing machines. Railcare Group AB (publ) was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Skelleftehamn, Sweden.
